#

Loaded Green Bean Casserole

45 min
$15
280 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 8

Allergens:

DairyOnion

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Side Dish

Tags:

Comfort FoodCasseroleEasyVegetarian

Description

A creamy and cheesy twist on the classic green bean casserole, loaded with flavor and topped with crispy onions.

Ingredients

  • green beans (fresh or frozen): 4 cups
  • cream of mushroom soup: 2 cans (10.5 oz each)
  • sour cream: 1 cup
  • shredded cheddar cheese: 2 cups
  • french fried onions: 1 cup
  • garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: 1/2 teaspoon
  • black pepper: 1/4 teaspoon
